{"tid":2490454,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"入黎傾下李克勤歌/事業","createTime":"2021-04-15T15:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:53:40.000Z","uid":25526,"like":10,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da8e46c2dda47cbe0a1f5e4a8878556defdbc437","tid":2490454,"uid":25526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"通常講李克勤大家會諗起送禮，不如傾下克勤既事業高低起跌，同埋佢d 歌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全盛時期嘅李克勤到底有幾紅？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2483523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2483523</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 克勤可唔可以開sidetrack 演唱會，歌迷等左好多年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f66a9bed17e84e693882c31cc904c6f8891fae","tid":2490454,"uid":25526,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"引返上一個d 內容先<br />\n<br />\n重溫其中一個神級現場 愛不釋手 2003年左麟右李版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由其2:04<br />\n誰亦明白火花終有日耗盡　但為何霎眼停了手<br />\n<br />\n有巴打話好有璀燦既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rko7pgBaqMk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRko7pgBaqMk&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=b4522021\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rko7pgBaqMk</a><br />\n<br />\n比一比較其他版本就知咩事，拎返同一句黎比較<br />\n<br />\n04 係2:02 開始<br />\n唔係唔好，但03 真係太神級 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UV1L-X-3Nao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUV1L-X-3Nao&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=5d2ea134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UV1L-X-3Nao</a><br />\n<br />\n最差既06年<br />\n無晒火花既火花<br />\n<br />\n1:56開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cbDkv1g68kM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcbDkv1g68kM&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=986b956d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cbDkv1g68kM</a><br />\n聽返11年，都係差左成條街，雖然已經好過06年<br />\n3:20<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v0VZh_z1Y4I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv0VZh_z1Y4I&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=d57b07a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v0VZh_z1Y4I</a> <br />\n<br />\n17年就唔post 啦，因為佢喊住黎唱唔可以作準<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下佢邊首歌邊個版本最好啦，上個post 有人講02 15 年月半小夜曲，04年我不會唱歌<br />\n<br />\n02 月半<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6FM7kARun4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6FM7kARun4w&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=c9dcc217\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6FM7kARun4w</a><br />\n15 月半<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NBrQaaEjYdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNBrQaaEjYdQ&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=5737da13\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NBrQaaEjYdQ</a><br />\n<br />\n04 我不會唱歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1k7xVmlO5bI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1k7xVmlO5bI&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=088bc45f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1k7xVmlO5bI</a>"},{"pid":"e48df615079ec32d379a8d24d3180d4cdd8f6235","tid":2490454,"uid":103833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"Sidetrack:白紙鶴 今天最愛 <br />\n<br />\n其實有好多唔係sidetrack 佢都好少唱 好似吻別的位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc31a2d94827ffaf3f7591ab0811764730d780c9","tid":2490454,"uid":25526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e48df615079ec32d379a8d24d3180d4cdd8f6235","tid":2490454,"uid":103833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"Sidetrack:白紙鶴 今天最愛 <br />\n<br />\n其實有好多唔係sidetrack 佢都好少唱 好似吻別的位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"btw 佢首吻別的位置同碟既那個應該是我好似係同一日錄既，所以聽落兩首好鬼似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打講嗰d 都係10年前，好似上post 都好少講10年後既作品，我覺得罪人隻碟其實ok 架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過無乜人講<br />\n<br />\n補link, 等唔太熟克勤歌既人都可以有興趣聽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RYAJ0FdhAs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRYAJ0FdhAs8&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=8eb22c0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RYAJ0FdhAs8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CnlHgKgjBLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCnlHgKgjBLQ&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=ac4d6281\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CnlHgKgjBLQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Bdrwyr7hf5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBdrwyr7hf5I&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=795189d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Bdrwyr7hf5I</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hUGmJH4siBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhUGmJH4siBY&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=62887ef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hUGmJH4siBY</a>"},{"pid":"7745fe77daccd41740f6b0b3a956a51f9fa0fda2","tid":2490454,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"一口氣唱一個都不能少果幾句"},{"pid":"fd7a8ef85295c3cd028665a96c43d6162f7c5e0f","tid":2490454,"uid":194143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"最鐘意佢唱有關婚姻嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n分岔口 紙婚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有種說不出的哀傷"},{"pid":"9c37d935e6003a101af154e80c89ba690be23eb1","tid":2490454,"uid":194143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"Side track 嚟講我鍾意常在你左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb15aa59669947323fe45e88b22b6de42922a002","tid":2490454,"uid":129039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"紙牌屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b8583b946f0774b308e4190ece2bb4c5027488","tid":2490454,"uid":103833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd7a8ef85295c3cd028665a96c43d6162f7c5e0f","tid":2490454,"uid":194143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"最鐘意佢唱有關婚姻嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n分岔口 紙婚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有種說不出的哀傷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"仲有首晚安 如何虔誠道晚安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢成日嘥哂林夕啲靚詞 好多都冇推"},{"pid":"6835b6c3af4c9e91664247fb62678eed2e62d802","tid":2490454,"uid":210140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"九月中的陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3256df51078d6d4055b3a17f39a7d47ccbf7995","tid":2490454,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"24城記<br />\n世界未日的早上<br />\n<br />\n少有覺得佢唱歌有感情嘅歌"},{"pid":"6aefc83ef9460a5f27a0cc97d53ad201a895d07a","tid":2490454,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"好戲之人"},{"pid":"8e8ec98b0b74133df6fd3ef354c6711100719084","tid":2490454,"uid":24863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:20:09.000Z","msg":"再一次想你<br />\n寫我深情<br />\n三千零一夜<br />\n信心保證<br />\n榮譽勳章<br />\n佳節<br />\n想你的舊名字 （以前失戀聽到想喊）<br />\n在一起卻很寂寞<br />\n情比紙薄<br />\nParis Hilton<br />\n<br />\n好想聽佢live果陣唱呢啲歌"},{"pid":"ad215760d5466e3d590041302d1b5c54840d60ae","tid":2490454,"uid":397207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:34:28.000Z","msg":"諗起殘酷一丁<br />\n我係咪好膚淺"},{"pid":"dbe292035499c1fef3027261c92e894ec12ad362","tid":2490454,"uid":24024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:35:58.000Z","msg":"Side track 推介幾首<br />\n<br />\n情比紙簿<br />\n時代廣場<br />\n世界末日的早上<br />\n榮譽勳章<br />\n兩人行<br />\n公主太子<br />\n萬年孤寂<br />\n寂寞嘍囉<br />\n冬暖夏涼<br />\n花落誰家"},{"pid":"369a26250773590a62ec5bae905671505b5c86f7","tid":2490454,"uid":24024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b3256df51078d6d4055b3a17f39a7d47ccbf7995","tid":2490454,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"24城記<br />\n世界未日的早上<br />\n<br />\n少有覺得佢唱歌有感情嘅歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:37:40.000Z","msg":"每次live唱愛不釋手都好有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次30週年演唱會唱命運符號 聽到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a90d11a26cbb0ed59754b895a5aafb59a4862a0","tid":2490454,"uid":24024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd7a8ef85295c3cd028665a96c43d6162f7c5e0f","tid":2490454,"uid":194143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"最鐘意佢唱有關婚姻嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n分岔口 紙婚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有種說不出的哀傷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:39:01.000Z","msg":"我鐘意佢唱關於社會民生議題嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n活著為求甚麼<br />\n二十四城記<br />\n天水圍城"},{"pid":"181739e00897faad093d0c34823172f682d8a04f","tid":2490454,"uid":393544,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:41:37.000Z","msg":"譚詠麟張學友之外唱功最好既歌手"},{"pid":"ad3f21a4408cc35545c5cf1505ce44a5bf25a103","tid":2490454,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T22:45:42.000Z","msg":"2004年拉闊<br />\n萬千寵愛在一身<br />\n習慣失戀"},{"pid":"255dea0f3d8f1dd4a60bab6a11ab260bc944b8cb","tid":2490454,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"我以前都成日J 愛不釋手火花嗰個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先成句好快咁爬個音階上去，要轉換音區已經難<br />\n<br />\n之後「火」字聲母個共鳴位比較入更難發力，而「花」字向出比較易比力，如果唔畀力亦會冇曬氣勢<br />\n<br />\n所以成句就係你技術/ 狀態唔好的話，個火字會想偷雞放輕唱就算，但就會令後面個花字都弱曬，樓上貼嘅幾個live嘅比較已經好清楚示範咗<br />\n<br />\n因為我自己都鍾意唱歌，哩個位都係花咗好多功夫先叫做克服到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d0d09a9397a76cba40ca6deeb9bc585cd9a678","tid":2490454,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T23:31:24.000Z","msg":"英雄故事<br />\n命運符號<br />\n雪女<br />\n只想你會意<br />\n九月中的陌生人<br />\n靜夜<br />\n為你流淚<br />\n如果一天<br />\n情迷心竅<br />\n冬暖夏涼<br />\n火柴<br />\n世界末日的早上<br />\n二十四城記"},{"pid":"0e3c2e20193bff1e312f7dc879d121fc1e674f57","tid":2490454,"uid":241832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbe292035499c1fef3027261c92e894ec12ad362","tid":2490454,"uid":24024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:35:58.000Z","msg":"Side track 推介幾首<br />\n<br />\n情比紙簿<br />\n時代廣場<br />\n世界末日的早上<br />\n榮譽勳章<br />\n兩人行<br />\n公主太子<br />\n萬年孤寂<br />\n寂寞嘍囉<br />\n冬暖夏涼<br />\n花落誰家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"好多都有plug喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc473a12dc826ad9253f0eea8a59194fdd50138f","tid":2490454,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"其實佢第一張大碟已經係高水準專輯<br />\n很多歌就算今日聽都好有意思"},{"pid":"ab7daff8bdbaccf10ea96eb3729312c6202b4106","tid":2490454,"uid":24863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢再開演唱會，簡簡單單一個琴，一支結他，一套鼓，好似之前MOOV 果個mini concert咁，輕輕鬆鬆咁唱已經好有feel。唔洗搞咁多花臣。"},{"pid":"4f0c5be778e7188d03748340f5fbf437db2acaaa","tid":2490454,"uid":103833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"復克有首句號好好loop"}]}